<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="<%= language === 'zh' ? 'zh-TW' : 'en' %>">
<head>
<!-- meta attributes -->
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="author" content="Jack Gowan">
<meta name="description" content="first built maze">
<title>The Maze - The Choice of Together</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/a_maze_style.css">
</head>
<body>
<h1 class="main-title"><%= translations?.[language]?.title || 'The Last Act' %></h1>

  <div class="room-container">
    <div class="content-wrapper">
      <div class="room-image">
        <img src="/images/z_give-up.png" alt="Giving up on the maze">
      </div>
      <div class="room-content">
    <div class="room-text">
      <code>
            <%- translations?.[language]?.text || `"So the only choice I have is to smash the crysal?" You inquire.
        <p>"Yes that is the only choice."</p>
        <p>"I give up" You plead. "This isn't what I after."</p>
        <p> "You have no choice sadly"</p>
        <p> And with that you slam the crystal to the floor shattering it to a 1000 pieces.</p>
        <p> Ahead a door appears. The light is warm, welcoming. You can feel it calling to you, promising not power or reward, but understanding. </p>` %>
          </code>
    </div>
    <hr/>

    <div class="navigation">
          <p><%= translations?.[language]?.choices?.prompt || 'Continue forward:' %></p>
          <a href="/maze/complete"><%= translations?.[language]?.choices?.options?.[0] || 'Step through to the end' %></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
